Source: avnav-meshtastic-plugin
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Unknown <unknown@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), python3, python3-pip
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: avnav-meshtastic-plugin
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, avnav, python3-serial, python3-pubsub
Description: AvNav plugin for Meshtastic radio integration
 Sends GPS position, environmental telemetry and alarm notifications
 via a Meshtastic LoRa device connected over USB serial.
 .
 Bundles the meshtastic Python library (2.7.7) and the dependencies that
 require newer versions than Raspbian Bookworm ships: bleak, dbus-fast,
 packaging, protobuf, tabulate, PyYAML, requests and their transitive
 dependencies.
 .
 pyserial and pypubsub are satisfied by the system deb packages
 python3-serial and python3-pubsub.
XB-avnav-plugin: meshtastic
